// =====================================================
// CONNECTIONS
// =====================================================

// Frontend Flow
Angular Client > Ocelot API Gateway : HTTP
Host Shell > Ocelot API Gateway : HTTP
Store MFE > Host Shell : Loads
Checkout MFE > Host Shell : Loads
Account MFE > Host Shell : Loads

// Gateway to Services
Ocelot API Gateway > Catalog API : Routes
Ocelot API Gateway > Basket API : Routes
Ocelot API Gateway > Ordering API : Routes

// Internal gRPC
Basket API > Discount API (gRPC) : gRPC

// Service to Database
Catalog API > catalogdb
Basket API > basketdb
Discount API (gRPC) > discountdb
Ordering API > orderdb

// S3 Storage
Catalog API > LocalStack S3 : Product Images

// Async Messaging
Basket API > RabbitMQ : Publish
RabbitMQ > Ordering API : Subscribe

// Logging
Catalog API, Basket API, Discount API (gRPC), Ordering API > Elasticsearch : Structured Logs
Elasticsearch > Kibana

// Metrics & Tracing
Microservices Layer > Prometheus : Metrics
Prometheus > Grafana
Microservices Layer > Jaeger : Traces
Istio Service Mesh > Kiali : Observability

// Kubernetes Orchestration
Container Orchestration > Microservices Layer : Deploys
Container Orchestration > Data Layer : Deploys
Container Orchestration > Infrastructure Services : Deploys
Container Orchestration > Monitoring Stack : Deploys
Admin MFE > Host Shell: [color: blue]
